   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Turn 300 children into Environmental Ambassadors</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We know that the environment must be protected because it&apos;s our source of life. Some of us have been taught how to protect it in school. However, this isn&apos;t the case in Kenya due to lack of a proper environmental education curriculum. MSI&apos;s project will take 300 primary school children in Nairobi, aged between 10-14 years old through a curriculum developed to equip them with knowledge and practical skills that they can use to conserve their environment turning them into Environmental Ambassadors</narrative>
  </description>
